Welcome to ${project.name}!

 Handle internationalization and localization easily with the i18n Maven Plugin. Convert your Excel sheets to resource files. Your input file i18n.xls will be converted to different output resource files. 
 To get started and see how the plugin could be used, check out this project documentation!  

